Package: synthesim
Title: Interactive Explorer for the MEDv4 Fitness-Fatigue Model
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jacob", "Bowie", email = "jacob.bowie2@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A deterministic forward-simulator for the MEDv4
    fitness-fatigue-signal ODE, with a Shiny + marimo explorer and a
    seven-test reference-mode validator anchored to canonical
    resistance-training literature. Models the three-stock structure
    Fitness/Fatigue/Signal driven by a TRIMP forcing function and
    exposes scenario builders for arbitrary periodization schemes
    (Renaissance Periodization mesocycles, return-from-break,
    detraining, custom event lists).
